Notes:
Arriving to STS Office
Please note we have two entrances for the Sun Tribe Solar office. One entrance is located off of Water Street. The Water Street entrance is a glass doorway located next to the Virginia National Bank Drive-Thru. The second entrance to our office is located off of 3rd Street. At this entrance you will enter the basement of the building, so take the elevator or stairwell to the 2nd floor.

Parking
Parking is available at Water Street Garage and Market Street Garage. Please note the Water Street Garage is located across the street from our office. Street Parking is available on 2nd Street, 6th Street, and Garrett Street. Jennifer Butler can provide a validation ticket (4 hours) to either garage if needed. 

Problems or concerns during travel? Feel free to text/call Jennifer Butler at (434) 906-2931.
